{
  "stem": "3022.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was no room to sit down, so we managed to design a way by which we would spread our legs, and the people would sit one next to the other.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There was no air, so we designed a rotation system where each and every one from the part of the car would stand at the little window for a while in the four corners.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "On the third day, it was so unbearable that we were drinking-- we were licking the salty condensation on the walls.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There was no toilet facilities, so we dug out with our hands a hole in the bottom of the train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Two people already took cyanide, committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we propped them up against the wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The nerves were so frail and so much on edge that fights were breaking out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "When we pulled out to a station in a large city, Nuremberg, and we stopped at the station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And there were some army nurses walking around, because there were transports of soldiers going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And all you could hear the cries of [GERMAN] through the windows, because this is already the third day we had no food, no water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And as fate wanted, Reb Meyer-- the one that I spoke about, that observant person-- was at one of the windows at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And he yelled out for water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And one of the nurses mercifully brought him a bottle of water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And he took it to the bars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And everybody in the car became very tense.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "The situation was-- you could cut the air.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And had he taken the bottle of water and drank from it, I'm sure that they would fallen upon him and tore it out of his hands.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
